  title="Yellow Grease Centrifuge"
  description="Dolphin Centrifuge offers yellow grease centrifuge case study: UCO collector replaced settling tanks with DMPX-042 disc stack — 8M gal/year, ROI under 6 months."
  category="applications"
  categoryLabel="Applications"
  canonicalUrl="https://dolphincentrifuge.com/yellow-grease-purification-centrifuge/"
