  <!-- ── Specifications ── -->
  <h2 id="specifications">DMPX-042 Specifications for Yellow Grease</h2>

  <p>
    The DMPX-042 is a high-capacity, self-cleaning 3-phase disc stack centrifuge. The following specifications apply to yellow grease processing at the recommended operating temperature of 180&deg;F.
  </p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Specification</th>
        <th>DMPX-042</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Type</td>
        <td>Self-Cleaning 3-Phase Disc Stack</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
